Package: soryos-archive-keyring
Version: 0.1.0
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: SoryOS Team <maintainers@soryos.local>
Description: SoryOS APT archive signing keyring
 This package installs the public SoryOS APT archive keyring for signed APT
 repository usage. It does not modify Pop!_OS repositories.
